xxl.core.indexStructures

Class HilbertRTreeBulkLoading

  • java.lang.Object
    • xxl.core.indexStructures.BPlusTreeBulkLoading
      • xxl.core.indexStructures.HilbertRTreeBulkLoading

  • public class HilbertRTreeBulkLoading
extends BPlusTreeBulkLoading
    This class provides functionality to bulk-load a HilbertRTree. The tree is created bottom-up.
